# -------------------------

**/node_modules
**/npm-debug.log
**/yarn-debug.log
**/yarn-error.log
**/pnpm-debug.log

# TypeScript
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Backend build output
backend/dist/

# Next.js build output
frontend/.next/

# Coverage
**/coverage/
**/.nyc_output/

